


Montreux-Palace Hotel

1820 Montreux, Switzerland

September 13, 1974

Dear Gleb Petrovich,

Forgive me for replying in English to your Russian letter of August 15th.

VN appreciates all the errors you catch in Field's Bibliography (although he still thinks that Field produced a valuable book in which he invested a lot of labor). We don't know who is Foster.1 It really does not matter, says V.V., what he (or she) included or left out of his (her) bibliography. But Field's was meant to cover t